OL,6,FThe owners of a seafront pub near
OL,7,FFareham say they remain 'totally
OL,8,Fcommitted' to rebuilding it after it
OL,9,Fwas completely gutted by a fire.
OL,11,FHowever, local people fear it will be
OL,12,Fyears before The Osborne View at Hill
OL,13,FHead will reopen.
OL,15,FLocal resident Rod Massingham said:
OL,16,F"We woke up at about 3 o'clock that
OL,17,Fmorning and I was attracted by a red
OL,18,Fglow on all my windows at the front of
OL,19,Fthe house. I looked out and to my
OL,20,Fastonishment the pub was absolutely
OL,21,Fablaze. It was an inferno."
