OL,6,F"The ferocity of the fire has caused
OL,7,Fmajor inconvenience and concern to the
OL,8,Flocal community, in some cases to a
OL,9,Fsignificant degree, and so I am truly
OL,10,Fthankful for the understanding of
OL,11,Fthose who have been affected.
OL,13,F"Their support at such a challenging
OL,14,Ftime is very much appreciated by all
OL,15,Fat Hall & Woodhouse.
OL,17,F"Our immediate priority has been to
OL,18,Fensure the personal wellbeing of
OL,19,Faffected team members, five of which
OL,20,Fwere resident on site at the time of
OL,21,Fthe fire.
