OL,6,F"These team members have been
OL,7,Frelocated to a hotel while we arrange
OL,8,Falternative longer-term accommodation,
OL,9,Fand we have also supported them in
OL,10,Fpurchasing necessities to replace
OL,11,Fthose lost in the fire.
OL,13,F"We are now finalising plans to
OL,14,Fprovide longer-term practical and
OL,15,Femotional support and will be liaising
OL,16,Fclosely with all those affected in the
OL,17,Fcoming days as we progress our
OL,18,Fassistance.
