OL,6,F"It is clear that due to the extent of
OL,7,Fthe fire, the original building has
OL,8,Fbeen sadly lost. I know that many
OL,9,Fpeople in the locality will also be
OL,10,Ffeeling the impact of the damage to
OL,11,Fthis much-loved neighbourhood asset.
OL,13,F"We will be closed for the foreseeable
OL,14,Ffuture, but we remain totally
OL,15,Fcommitted to rebuilding The Osborne
OL,16,FView as a pub and to our part in the
OL,17,Flocal community in the long term. We
OL,18,Fwill update on plans when we are able."
